  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1c44d26bee7f894782729c6bcff2b73, type: 3}
  m_Name: Chives Conversation 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  SpeakerName: Yukio
  paragraphs:
  - 'yawwwwwnnn...

    Really? Chives?


    You just let your talents go to waste
    sometimes.'
  - What? I was trying something new okay...
  - "Yeah well, don\u2019t\n\n*yawwwwns*\n\nGod I want to have a nap now"
  - Not before you tell me about your night, did you do what I asked?
  - 'Fine.


    But yes of course I did because I am great at what I do'
  - I got in contact with Kenji - the detective you remember
  - Of course
  - Right, well this guy was really strange but he agreed without hesitation
  - At this point so many detectives have turned us down this guy could be anyone
    and I would hire him
  - 'Thank god, and I agree, I have waited too long already. '
  - I miss him
  - Its okay Yukio, I am always here for you
  - ...
  - Except for right now, I got things (and the girl from last night) to do
  - Right, have fun with that
  - "Bye! \n\nNext time PLEASE feed me something less boring"
